,{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"title":"OUDSSuggestionChip","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip/accessibilityLabel(_:isEnabled:)-7t9fz":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/accessibilityLabel(_:isEnabled:)-7t9fz","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"accessibilityLabel"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI18LocalizedStringKeyV","text":"LocalizedStringKey"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"isEnabled"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI15ModifiedContentV","text":"ModifiedContent"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Self"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s